{"tid":1683060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王喜鬧爆警察用白卡","createTime":"2019-10-30T12:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T13:48:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5d10f9d0637257151174da9dffadf813330395e9","tid":1683060,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191030/20796288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796288&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHtRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=37ed3098\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796288&h=726141a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191030/20796288</a><br />\n<br />\n王喜鬧爆警察用白卡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191030/large/1572354235_69c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191030%2Flarge%2F1572354235_69c7.jpg&h=83dd02b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王喜昨日在fb上大鬧警方的白卡，收工就會變成廢紙。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n在香港主權移交前曾任皇家香港警察的王喜，多次在社交網鬧爆警方。警方最近以一張印上行動呼號的白色硬卡，代替警員委任證編號，王喜昨日在fb鬧爆：「乜＿行動代號呀？同囚犯一樣，你哋每一個都被分配一個終生編號，由入冊到出殯，去到邊，叫一聲呢個冧巴，就等如叫你。」王喜又指：「卡紙可以當塔羅牌咁，今日你抽呢張嚟當更，收工就變廢紙，聽日又再抽過第二張。日日換代號，過得兩、三月，你有本事記得全部用過嘅代號咩？」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【兄弟爬山】譚小環「助養」抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191030/large/1572354235_9005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191030%2Flarge%2F1572354235_9005.jpg&h=e5caa77a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方周日以印上有行動呼號的白色硬卡代替委任證。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n另外，《野獸刑警》編劇陳慶嘉上周五以筆名阿寬為報章撰寫專欄，他以「最優秀警察」為題，大讚毅進畢業的警察，勝過美國哈佛大學的醫學博士。陳慶嘉昨日接受電話訪問，他笑說︰「讚下啲警察啦，佢哋做得咁好、咁叻，佢哋應該唔會驕傲嘅。」至於警察最弱一環「唔曉講大話」，他慨嘆說︰「每日見記者會都俾人拆穿，市民都『好錫』佢哋，指出有乜嘢錯。」憑《野》片獲影帝的黃秋生大讚陳慶嘉：「果然係文人，好鬼抵死。警察出嚟搞笑箒，同講大話乜關係都冇，反過嚟解讀，全部真話。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：李森 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n網民籲搵紅星發聲 天佑：邊個當紅<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n新光周六日夜場變日場<br />\n<br />\n【兄弟爬山】譚小環「助養」抗爭者<br />\n愛國馬蹄露斥海洋公園推卸責任<br />\n網民籲搵紅星發聲 天佑：邊個當紅<br />\n新光周六日夜場變日場<br />\n【娛樂人物】旺角開店蝕入肉吳日言無懼催淚彈 落區救亡"},{"pid":"0078333df30f37fe89c1362e53b42b74a262638b","tid":1683060,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5220696ab5bae094c387ffbd2c1d7b7d62820bfc","tid":1683060,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"陳導演曲過殺神特工最後安祖自殺果粒子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8c5200097250cb448aca0c7ffefe5f65cd92e8","tid":1683060,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> /Task1</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHtRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=5b13bb0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"}]}